{"tid":1578214,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬會取消所有賽事 今晚區議員會有對話會","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T05:28:54.000Z","uid":128430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e08b68695e1fe2c6f1e497cf1f6b95ba3b8b9a7b","tid":1578214,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"反對修訂《逃犯條例》風波觸發多場暴力衝突，立法會議員何君堯在7月21日的元朗衝突中，與「白衫軍」握手引起爭議，成為風波中的惹火人物，其愛駒亦恐受牽連，何君堯名下的「天祿」今晚(18日)在跑馬地馬場出賽，有網民發起今晚圍堵跑馬地馬場，香港賽馬會嚴陣以待，決定取消今晚所有賽事。<br />\n何君堯的愛駒「天祿」今晚參加的二班賽事，罕有獲編於第一場舉行，原定今晚7時15分開跑。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家留意：今晚政府總部 區議員對話會</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4be5d31c7575138aa205228e90103bf044b25ce","tid":1578214,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"641b96204e9547b77d11eb3b07a873c235a4fd32","tid":1578214,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a hr